Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但我看  像是有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}To me, it was like someone was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想表达什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}having a conversation, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,92年  那女孩的学校关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}Girl's... school shut down in '92.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁事件之后就关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}It closed down after Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你们有用吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}That mean anything to you?
