Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们亲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}Did they have a relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么问  你们听说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}Why? What have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说他过世了  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}I heard he passed. Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么父亲不给自己的孩子洗澡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}Why wouldn't a father bathe his own child?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}We, uh, we were just wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们关系好不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}how they got on, ma'am.
