Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,下高速时开得太快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}and he took an exit too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在俄克拉荷马州罗宛镇附近翻车了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}Rolled over near Rowan, Oklahoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,1984年  5月11日的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}May 11, 1984.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你最后一次跟她说话时什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}When was the last time you talked to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她总是有各种各样的麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}You know, she's always been in some kind of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我原以为事情有所好转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}I thought things were getting better.
