Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只说了她一直去教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}Said she'd been going to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}Do you, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得那教堂在哪里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}do you remember where that church was?
