Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,把我指甲搞成这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}That's what's wrong with my nails.
