Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没  说过一点关于他父亲的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}No. Little bit about his dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拉斯加  越南战争之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}Alaska, 'Nam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸  我比他高15厘米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}You know, my dad, I had about 6 inches on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但哪怕是他弥留的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\1c&H3CF1F3&}{\shad1}and even in the end,
